  "text": "Eight-micron-thick sections were cut from formalin-fixed paraffin-embedded blocks of the tumor and normal thyroid tissue, stained with nuclear fast red and microdissected under a stereomicroscope as previously described [CITATION_1] to ensure >80% of tumor cells content and that the normal tissue was devoid of neoplastic cells. RNA and genomic DNA were extracted and quantified as previously described [CITATION_2] .",
